##Â Search Rats [GET /rats]

Search records of rats by matching fields

::: warning
The search API does not yet work with nested objects, like drilled - dispatch, or nicknames. See [Rat search API does not work with nested objects in queries. #30](https://github.com/FuelRats/api.fuelrats.com/issues/30) for progress
:::

Scope: public

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes
      + platform: `xb` (boolean) - Return rats that are on Xbox One
      + drilled: (Drilled) - Return rats that have not been drilled

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
      + links (Link) - Links
      + meta (Meta) - Statistics on the current result
      + data (array[Rat]) - A list of rats
